Who is it?

17:07.814 --> 17:09.048
Madalena: It's me.

17:09.049 --> 17:11.215
Madalena?

17:11.217 --> 17:13.417
Don't be so dramatic. I just want to talk.

17:14.820 --> 17:15.920
Open the gate.

17:22.529 --> 17:24.762
Stay!

17:24.763 --> 17:26.498
[Gate closes]

17:26.499 --> 17:29.702
Well, what do we have here?

17:29.703 --> 17:30.803
Galavant.

17:30.804 --> 17:33.305
Richard.

17:33.306 --> 17:34.339
You.

17:35.842 --> 17:36.975
