Our story lines
have been far too separated.

17:41.781 --> 17:43.449
Come on, babe. Let's go.

17:43.450 --> 17:45.216
You lied to me.

17:47.454 --> 17:48.687
No, but now I've come for you

17:48.688 --> 17:50.255
