than join the dark forces.

18:22.489 --> 18:24.123
Me too.

18:24.124 --> 18:25.891
- And me.
- And me.

18:25.892 --> 18:29.461
Right, well, no one invited you lot,
but whatever.

18:29.462 --> 18:31.230
[Sighs] Right.

18:31.231 --> 18:34.032
Well, I wasn't going to get
all sappy, but, um...

18:34.033 --> 18:35.567
Thanks for the adventure.

18:35.568 --> 18:37.069
Thanks for the power.

18:37.070 --> 18:38.903
Thanks for the crown.

18:42.976 --> 18:44.642
Thanks for the love.

18:47.981 --> 18:50.015
And since we're all such good friends,

18:50.016 --> 18:52.718
I will give you exactly 10 seconds.

18:52.719 --> 18:55.287
I suggest focusing
all your attention on sealing

18:55.288 --> 18:57.488
[clicks tongue] That door.

18:59.759 --> 19:01.659
Gareth...

19:02.862 --> 19:04.796
this is your last chance.

19:06.199 --> 19:08.966
[Somber music plays]

19:12.739 --> 19:14.939
No.

19:18.411 --> 19:21.045
Suit yourself.

19:23.082 --> 19:24.450
Out the way!

19:24.451 --> 19:27.119
[Horn blows]

19:27.120 --> 19:31.823
[Zombies shouting]

19:36.963 --> 19:39.598
This is it.

19:39.599 --> 19:40.899
We're going to die.

19:40.900 --> 19:42.901
Richard, stand behind me.

19:42.902 --> 19:43.902
I will not.

19:43.903 --> 19:46.371
I will stand beside you.

19:46.372 --> 19:48.073
♪

