♪ It's a good day to die ♪

19:50.577 --> 19:52.878
♪ We won't, there's one more episode ♪

19:52.879 --> 19:55.481
♪ But still, we could die ♪

19:55.482 --> 19:57.583
♪ We all know that's a massive load of... ♪

19:57.584 --> 19:58.984
Right.

19:58.985 --> 20:01.253
♪ Still, we might ♪

